CONSTANTS (module level): MAGIC = b"DSPC"; CODEC_NONE=0x00, CODEC_GZIP=0x01, CODEC_ZLIB=0x02. Import gzip, zlib, pickle at top.

Cache.__init__ new params (add after memory_max_entries, before the trailing comma/closing paren): 
  compress: Optional[str] = None,   # one of 'gzip', 'zlib', None
